{"tid":236971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片]被逼遷雪糕店主 : 再開店始終想喺深水埗","createTime":"2017-05-10T05:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T05:38:01.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c364126e58cfb58b0360b7121e7ddb22bc095fc0","tid":236971,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T05:37:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-6pBCTIcSPc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-6pBCTIcSPc&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=58abe73c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-6pBCTIcSPc</a><br />\n<br />\n被西九龍中心拒絕續租的雪糕店，連日來獲大批網民留言支持，又批評西九做法不當。對於因結業而引發的「災難」，傍晚，本刊再找來店主Calvin回應。<br />\n<br />\nCalvin首先感謝各位支持，他指雪糕店被廣泛報導後，每晚為滿足全部顧客，更要做到十二點才收工。結業在即，至今仍未得到西九龍中心任何回覆，Calvin直言這是預計之內，「他都不會覆我，希望做得一日得一日。」他又指已看過道歉啟事，但不認為有向他道歉的意思，「根本是他們自找麻煩，又要上載別人的新聞。」Calvin又稱西九只是選擇性撐小店，並非偉大。<br />\n<br />\n另外，對於有雪糕店稱被冤枉，Calvin説自己從未沒開名是那一間，「他們有沒有投訴自己心裡有數，其他人怎樣説我管不了。」至於再開店，Calvin承認已有商場跟他聯絡，不過自己還是鍾情深水埗。<br />\n<br />\n撰文:何紫<br />\n攝影:海江田"},{"pid":"0377cf86f4f8dd1bffdd9743e5e53a5b96ba6616","tid":236971,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T05:38:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20170509/509067\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20170509%2F509067&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d9583d72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20170509%2F509067&h=e036399c\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20170509/509067</a>"}]}